                Nonius Rufinianus et Tigra<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>a cum conpare <lb n="2"/>sua sibi fecerunt domum <expan><abbr>aeternale</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> dulcissimo filio <lb n="3"/>Proiecticio qui reque<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">scit</supplied> <note>sic</note> in pace annorum <lb n="4"/>X <expan><abbr>men</abbr><ex>sium</ex></expan> III <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ierum</ex></expan> XIIII <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omino</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostro</ex></expan> Arcadio</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> VI et Petronio <lb n="2"/>Anicio Probo <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>conss</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tafel aus 3 Fragmenten zusammengesetzt. Material: prokonnesischer Marmor. (B): Z. 4: d(ierum) XIII - AE 1983; AE 1977: reques[cit], sonst unvollständiger.</p>
